games.comment: Peyton Manning didn't play in the preseason and consequently was rusty, as he went 30-of-49, 257 yards and 1 touchdown, giving him a pedestrian YPA of 5.2, which is abysmal by his standards. Earlier in the day,
Peyton Manning, don't I? The narrative per the media will be that Manning stepped in for a struggling Brock Osweiler and saved the day to claim the division.
